wiki.summary: "Wave of Mutilation" is the third track on the Pixies' 1989 album, Doolittle.

track.name: Wave of Mutilation
comments: Not sure if I prefer this or the UK surf version. They're both great versions of a beautiful song.
Here's a fun early acoustic demo plus a cute extract from an interview http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g5qXZqTVS7E
I cannot put into words how good of a song this is. Lyrically and musically perfect.
If you're listening to the surf mix, than this version is waaaay too fast!
Walked the sand with the crustaceans.
You think I'm dead but I sail away on a wave of mutilation.
Drive my car into the ocean.
